column1: Bitcoin critic Sen. Menendez faces federal bribery allegations
column2: U.S. Senator Bob Menendez, a prominent critic of Bitcoin's adoption in El Salvador, finds himself amid a federal bribery scandal. The New Jersey Democrat and Chairman of the Foreign Relations Committee, a powerhouse position in the Senate, now faces allegations of questionable relationships with local business moguls.
